{"tid":311033,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[點評]岩岩睇完只有我不存在的街道......","createTime":"2017-07-06T09:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T14:16:18.000Z","uid":21000,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9836a4eb32dce87ba9ec836fec89b963e35413da","tid":311033,"uid":21000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"Hello 又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為最近實在太多野做無時間出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為之前有巴打話想睇下我評只有我不存在的城市 所以就試下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔多講 開波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劇情 : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劇情合理 節奏緊湊 高潮常有 因為悟係成程入面都有個好清楚既目標同埋觀眾會知佢做緊咩事 令到更容易可以follow up個進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先講下係劇情方面既優點<br />\n1. 上面講左一個劇情合理 節奏緊湊<br />\n2. 好刻意咁為唔同角色留低左可疑既地方 觀眾就會好自然因為見到咁多疑犯而去一齊思考推理 投入度高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雖然到後期幾乎都會估到個犯就係老師</span></span><br />\n3. 有好多細微位都照顧到 : 細心睇就會發現悟佢穿越得耐左就越適應細佬仔既身份 最易見到既地方就係有一集悟同佢啲朋友講byebye果陣好大動作好細佬咁fing哂幾野手<br />\n4. 有好多細微位都照顧到(2) : 就係當悟佢穿越返去細個果陣內心獨白用既大人聲 但訓左15年醒返之後內心獨白係用返小朋友聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 好表達到細佬仔既心態同純真 無論係言語定行動上 最明顯睇到既地方我覺得係悟同加代係公園合掌果到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁當然 缺點方面都有 : <br />\n1. 個gay end<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗唔少巴打都會覺個gay end 太突兀 同前面既故事對比起黎 雖然佢有個好正經既解釋但係都兜唔到個咁既結局<br />\n2. 呢套野個名叫只有我不存在的街道 有兩個意思 一個就係加代細個比人虐待果陣作既文 另一個就係講悟訓左15年既果段時間<br />\n前者問題不大 問題就在於後者<br />\n睇過就會知後者既解釋係出現係結尾 係解因為自己訓左15年 係呢段時間入面朋友為佢付出左人生入面寶貴既時間 所以係佢既寶物<br />\n但問題係動畫入面又無講太多朋友為佢付出左幾多時間 做左啲咩 <br />\n令到觀眾好難有一個更加深刻既印象<br />\n3. 個人覺得第2次再上映返細個果次有啲兒戲 整體小左啲緊張感 因為再唔係行錯一步就玩撚猿<br />\n4. 個人想佢有多啲推理既情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 加代同廣美結左婚 屌你老母 難得我對佢開始有小小咁多好感 佢同我嫁撚左比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能有巴打話悟只係救加代 唔算情侶唔算ntr 但都唔係比佢嫁撚左比個不男不女既人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亦都有講其他現象黎加深整體深度例如對夢想既追求, 對窮人既偏見, 校園欺凌, 為適應社會而演繹內心理想既自己, 家庭暴力 更甚本身講緊既兒童失蹤都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整體黎講係唔差既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作畫 : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n崩圖甚少 畫風還可 而每個角色面型都係偏包 一開頭睇得唔太慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他地方都做得幾好 例如穿越左係上下有黑間 真係好似&quot;上映&quot;咁 而現實就會正正常常咁<br />\n另外分鏡方面都做幾好 可能我孤陋寡聞 但最震撼我既係有一幕係隻烏鴉咬緊果對未織完既手套 睇到真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人設 : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人設方面其實我覺得稍有不足 但畢竟呢套係一套劇情向動畫 無可能求佢面面俱圓 人物既性格特徵都可以係佢地既對話入面睇到 但因為描寫唔太多同無咩特別 所以就唔多落墨水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n音樂 : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nop ed還可 但唔係我既風格都唔係我想講既重點<br />\n重點係佢入面既配樂好到位 幫成套作品營造到緊張 懸疑 神秘既氣氛 呢方面做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令人睇得好投入 我有幾個位都睇到差啲嗌左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結局 : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面雖然已經講左個結局太虧 但我覺得都唔錯係因為好睇到悟既轉變 佢由一開始係個失敗既毒撚 仲比漫畫社果條人話作品入面睇唔到佢既痕跡 但係係佢解開咁多年既心結 終於救到加代, 同朋友好好咁相處返, 決定真心對人. 最後終於有佢之前無既勇氣同同伴 令到自己係最後終於完整<br />\n係重新成長下終於有一個完整既自己 個人覺得呢到唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總結 : 客觀黎講我覺得呢套算係一套佳作 但唔知點解我主觀又覺得佢未去到咁既程度因為佢有種講唔出口既怪(我由打呢篇文開始已經咁覺得但打完仲係唔識形容)同埋對比起命運石之門好似硬係差咁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實到底係叫街道定係城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n另外想知你地覺得四月新番有邊套覺得好睇 求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">岩岩睇完兩套唔知係我太攰睇唔明定我中間隔開左一段時間睇 覺得麻麻地</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea0740f203e706f04a317941611859dbffe518bf","tid":311033,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"評 正確的卡多"},{"pid":"9bfd09c296dfcbfb6927f17552ef580077e1ae73","tid":311033,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"乜個end 係gay咩<br />\nBtw評得幾好"},{"pid":"5681ce914ea68d361a7ad85b115db528c9c9fec2","tid":311033,"uid":95413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"只有我被ntr的街道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實op ed聽多幾次覺得幾正<br />\n<br />\nbtw下套你諗住睇咩"},{"pid":"e8e53666047c648c839ae8d8b891b8f5fb9d042e","tid":311033,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"日文原文：僕だけがいない街<br />\n<br />\n日文街字係指多商戶個啲地方（好似係<br />\n<br />\n總之街道定城講 就係譯名問題"},{"pid":"053bae671d154de78d0aa8814e24b32a7a7eedff","tid":311033,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:48:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得套劇劇情講主角拯救女主角，想令佢幸福 偏向情感類<br />\n多過懸疑搵凶手係邊個，所以估到凶手都唔太影響觀感"},{"pid":"68986905c2f1849a54af883fe762f968d3a63fb0","tid":311033,"uid":21000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>評 正確的卡多</blockquote><br />\n好 睇埋手頭上幾套先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc40ad4ccc004ee07039f5f1a4d4248c43589d84","tid":311033,"uid":21000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜個end 係gay咩<br />\nBtw評得幾好</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算唔gay都有啲突兀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aef86bfa74e7ab3ca42c185c735a944d167f0ee","tid":311033,"uid":21000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只有我被ntr的街道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實op ed聽多幾次覺得幾正<br />\n<br />\nbtw下套你諗住睇咩</blockquote><br />\nNo game no life <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後有月色真美 不起眼女主角培育法第二季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be07a038ef8da4b15637d72ea10d7a3cf28e4c2","tid":311033,"uid":21000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得套劇劇情講主角拯救女主角，想令佢幸福 偏向情感類<br />\n多過懸疑搵凶手係邊個，所以估到凶手都唔太影響觀感</blockquote><br />\n一半半啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢前段比較似為救而救 到中段小小先係想佢幸福<br />\n而佢係前中期可以將感情同推理既比例排得岩岩好我都好欣賞<br />\n而就算估到係老師 係揭佢就係鬼果下都好震撼 的確唔影響觀感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申半個月前睇完 記錯唔好屌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8720b9de95bebf66b3015510411e4d7250398293","tid":311033,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"成個故事印象最深係一條安全帶係可以kick住一個小學生"},{"pid":"78b93e250c5bceaadd6ebc507cce9e6e0a5be129","tid":311033,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"結尾怪係呢個作者既弊病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過條友講故功力勁<br />\n引到人想追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bea69288f182bda7ca1207c81f32188d03c7a3","tid":311033,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"識評梗係要評 人渣的本願 啦"},{"pid":"724dac958c541cd97d66ab5f8a29c4c4ea887264","tid":311033,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結尾怪係呢個作者既弊病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過條友講故功力勁<br />\n引到人想追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOh<br />\n原來你睇動畫版<br />\n呢套我反而會推番人睇漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200fd6333f8f56d483f654242c9a00a45752baa6","tid":311033,"uid":66076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"高質巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac71a6efac1d34e7b06f6bf7b32e5cc63db96db4","tid":311033,"uid":21000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個故事印象最深係一條安全帶係可以kick住一個小學生</blockquote><br />\n小學生姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><s