ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主淨係睇完動畫就出嚟評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動畫細節又cut晒，end又垃圾，睇完根本唔算睇晒成個故事"},{"pid":"5e29e3075e0a77b0aa5ad475e7ac58ce6109d4d7","tid":311033,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:27:58.000Z","msg":"有睇埋漫畫就知悟訓左既時候<br />\n個偽娘取代左悟本來既生活<br />\n所以如果悟冇訓到既話<br />\n加代其實係同悟一齊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85c6fb4cfe6c7674fedee8ae781fc9867c3bd62","tid":311033,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"建議樓豬加返［動畫］兩隻字<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係又比人入架喇"},{"pid":"a950307a347e11867253a7877a421f664fc35f0d","tid":311033,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"係sad都係sad重映完同愛莉無左關係啦<br />\n<br />\n根本加代就唔屬於男豬<br />\n<br />\n男豬只係盡返人道 想救返佢<br />\n<br />\n如果任何人都有重映<br />\n刷好感度根本就唔成問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男豬救完佢就昏迷 正正就係講左<br />\n如果單純剩係改變左佢死既事實<br />\n佢最後生存到 係會同偽娘一齊<br />\n<br />\n只係因為有一命之恩就要人以身相許 等個唔知醒唔醒到既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b96fa2310631a021969ac030bf6f7cd8b7fbef","tid":311033,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識評梗係要評 人渣的本願 啦</blockquote><br />\n評ed 起我底就見到有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867628b12be07870c58876dc74f65737c2946914","tid":311033,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:43:33.000Z",